ElementLabel:
One or more of the orders to be approved need to be prioritised because they contain one of the following:
  • Interim Care Order
  • Emergency Protection Order
  • Exclusion Order
  • Recovery Order
  • Child Assessment Order
  • Port Alert Order
  • Passport Order
  • Non-Molestation Order
  • Occupation Order
If the order does not contain one of the orders above, leave blank and continue.
